headline: SBA Communications: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The real estate investment trust, based in Boca Raton, Florida, said it had funds from operations of $340.4 million, or $3.19 per share, in the period. The average estimate of four analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $3.25 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.

headline: SBA Communications Corporation Reports Fourth Quarter 2025 Results; Provides Full Year 2026 Outlook; and Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: BOCA RATON, Fla., February 26, 2026--SBA Communications Corporation (Nasdaq: SBAC) ("SBA" or the "Company") today reported results for the quarter ended December 31, 2025.
